These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-1::.
City: boston, hamburg
The people have 2 different hobbies: skydiving, reading
1. the person traveling to hamburg is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| City           | hamburg | boston |
| Hobby   | reading     | skydiving  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-2::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: writing, camping
City: edinburgh, hamburg
1. the person traveling to edinburgh is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is writing##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |     2     |
| Hobby         | camping   | writing      |
| City   | edinburgh | hamburg |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-3::.
City: boston, san-francisco
