.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-16::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: western, documentary
The people have 2 different hobbies: drawing, baking
1. the person who's hobby is baking is somewhere to the left of the person watching western movies##5
2. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |
| Movie-Genre      | documentary        | western  |
| Hobby   | baking | drawing |

